OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FHead brings in mother to   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fhelp cash-strapped school  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A head teacher said he had been forced 
OL,6, to ask his mother and sister to help   
OL,7, out due to a lack of staff.            
OL,9,FSteve Hitchcock, of St Peter's Primary 
OL,10,Fin Budleigh Salterton, Devon, said he  
OL,11,Fwas losing some catering staff to      
OL,12,Fsupermarkets because they paid more.   
OL,14,F"It does feel like something needs to  
OL,15,Fgive, enough is enough," he said.      
OL,17,FThe Department for Education said it   
OL,18,Funderstood that schools were facing    
OL,19,Fcost pressures and said they would     
OL,20,Fbenefit from the Energy Relief Scheme. 
